General.Name: Bredband2 i Skandinavien AB
General.Description: Bredband2 i Skandinavien AB (publ) provides data and telecommunications, and security solutions to individuals and companies in Sweden. It offers router subscriptions, security packages, streaming, network telephony comprising mobile telephony, internet services, mobile broadband, and data center services. The company was incorporated in 1989 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.
